{"tid":2046481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大S，關你甚麼事？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-06-01T12:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb35e7f5ac7fcb6b7c2d626bd6b801c5df51da72","tid":2046481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200601/20928399/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200601%2F20928399%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=fcc1b034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200601%2F20928399%2F&h=21ee1765\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200601/20928399/</a><br />\n<br />\n大S，關你甚麼事？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200601/large/1590910814_b889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200601%2Flarge%2F1590910814_b889.jpg&h=6ea41e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n約3000藝人聯名簽署支持中共在港推行《國安法》，大S徐熙媛竟然榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n一個台灣藝人，嫁了一個中國男人，留在中國賺人民幣。香港人跟她河水不犯井水，她以甚麼身份去簽署支持這條跟香港前途、香港人命運休戚相關的惡法？如果她是香港人，她歡迎這條惡法，那是她表達她的個人意願，那是她的選擇。可她不是香港人，幾時輪到她出聲？<br />\n<br />\n出生在民主國家，選擇做極權國家的奴隸，本身已經夠墮落。但她墮落只是她個人的事，香港人並不關心她的命運。。。。。。。。。。。。。。本防疫用品，足見這個人的人品多麼低劣。沒想到現在更墮落到簽名支持《港區國安法》，為一點點個人利益去支持一個地區由民主、開放、文明、法治走向極權與封閉。<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，大S回應指「是同名同姓」。香港娛樂圈究竟有沒有一個叫「徐熙媛」的人，就要請教娛樂記者及一眾八卦觀眾了。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"11f9c2f97f7d949e47e36a43280c8044e3ae3d91","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"都無計<br />\n佢嫁中國人<br />\n賺中國錢 成個世界甘心做奴隸<br />\n係香港人先咁有志氣嘅姐"},{"pid":"aebb093d9aefaaed091292478ba51323a6d6bc09","tid":2046481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f9c2f97f7d949e47e36a43280c8044e3ae3d91","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"都無計<br />\n佢嫁中國人<br />\n賺中國錢 成個世界甘心做奴隸<br />\n係香港人先咁有志氣嘅姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱三不館都有講呢件事"},{"pid":"b14b1df07a69005451c9a1e922e0f88d24277bef","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aebb093d9aefaaed091292478ba51323a6d6bc09","tid":2046481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f9c2f97f7d949e47e36a43280c8044e3ae3d91","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"都無計<br />\n佢嫁中國人<br />\n賺中國錢 成個世界甘心做奴隸<br />\n係香港人先咁有志氣嘅姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱三不館都有講呢件事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"我去望下先"},{"pid":"61d19eff288b0634a8e98a09c6b39d0f17bc6390","tid":2046481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b14b1df07a69005451c9a1e922e0f88d24277bef","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aebb093d9aefaaed091292478ba51323a6d6bc09","tid":2046481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f9c2f97f7d949e47e36a43280c8044e3ae3d91","tid":2046481,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"都無計<br />\n佢嫁中國人<br />\n賺中國錢 成個世界甘心做奴隸<br />\n係香港人先咁有志氣嘅姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱三不館都有講呢件事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"我去望下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"一開波就講"},{"pid":"8d8443a0e61ecc85a900abe2a33d67729133d310","ti